{"tid":1748072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔洗休假］葵芳交通警因眼短暫失去視力宜家放緊有薪病假！！","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:12:36.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7d9391ac997ca21ef0209c5ee03688d767d78c","tid":1748072,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"蘋果今日就相關事件向警察公共關係科跟進，問及案件調查進度，涉案警員是否已結束休假並需接受處分，同時是否再度出任前線工作，而休假期間是否獲支薪，警察公共關係科傍晚時回應指，案件交由新界南總區交通部調查及支援組跟進，涉事警員當日執勤時遇襲受傷，目前正放取病假，強調警隊非常重視人員的操守，調查後如發現有任何違紀行為，必定嚴肅處理。消息指，涉案警員在事件後，一直報稱前臂遭打傷。警察公共關係科總警司謝振中當日於例行記者會上指，當時一名警員被不明化學品噴面，眼部短暫失去視力，然後該名駕駛電單車的警員上前支援，「試圖將暴徒同警察分隔」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2594839690602838?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2594839690602838%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=a3b0bba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2594839690602838?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"798b25e646b7857795e07bcaa84e6b859c270b9f","tid":1748072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"下。。。"},{"pid":"de0ac0238c6addbd351066ac0af79e6f38b63410","tid":1748072,"uid":36287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"盲既揸車做交通警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636d85c568e90d1250a48a5f4fca3722b74165ec","tid":1748072,"uid":16534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:55:34.000Z","msg":"最後直路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[人手頂置]連登區選最後共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745825/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745825/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"24e695f2b8fae53d6bfc853d19717812e93e7dc7","tid":1748072,"uid":269500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb7d9